I just played with my new Game Boy Advanced and
Nintendo is here to stay.  I don't even like racing
games, but for some reason that's what my parents got
me (F-Zero).  Still the graphics and sound alone were
enough to keep me enticed (none of those crummy little
speakers). Gamecube is just to keep Nintendo fans from
rioting.  This thing is as good as my old SNES.  By
the way do you realize I made this before Zardus
banned me for 2 months?
